.TH LOA-LIST-LANGUAGE 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
list language \- Show books filtered by language
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> list language <name>
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Filters books by one language and shows matching entries.
.TP
Supported language values are: German, English, French, Japanese.
.TP
Language matching is case-insensitive.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> list language german
.TP
alexandria> list language Japanese
